com.dselent.bigarraylist

Class FileAccessor<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.dselent.bigarraylist.FileAccessor<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - Generic type

    class FileAccessor<E>
extends java.lang.Object
    Class that reads and writes the contents of the BigArrayList to/from disk. Each BigArrayList is given a unique identifier so multiple BigArrayList objects can be used at once.

    The files are names with the following convention

    (filePath)(memory instance)"_memory_"(file/block number)(file extension)

    Examples:
    "memory\0_memory_0.jobj
    "memory\0_memory_1.jobj

    Author:
    Douglas Selent
